##Project Title
Eevee Evelution Guide 

##Concept 
For my project, I want to create an application that teaches people about Eevee and the evolutions that it can evolve into. 
This app will allow a user to select an evelution or an eevee and learn the basic information about it. Information that you can learn
about it is but not limited to type, how it evolves, and a small desription 

I chose this concept because I really enjoy Eevee and the evolutions that come along with Eevee. Pokemon is one of my favorite things and I 
wanted to base this project around my favorite one. 

##Goal 
The goal of this project is to build an easy to use program that helps users learn about Eevee and its evolutions. 
